data.description: Check out this amazing split level home at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac! This 5 bed / 3 bath + bonus room / office home greets you with an open main level-  including a formal gathering space, kitchen and dining room who's sliding patio doors open to your spacious fully fenced-in yard. Head down 3 steps to your family room with a full size bar for entertaining. Continue walking down the hall past 2 bedrooms to gain access to your 2 car garage. Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms with the Master bedroom having a full en-suite master bath.  All appliances are only about 3 years old. The seller has also allocated funds for a new roof to be put on in the spring. So all you would just have to do is pick your color and the job will be completed as soon as the weather warms back up.
